name: Hotel SM Deccan Park
description:
Looking for a place to stay in Hyderabad? Then look no further than Hotel Deccan Park, a budget friendly hotel that brings the best of Hyderabad to your doorstep.
You’ll enjoy relaxing rooms that offer a refrigerator, air conditioning, and a sofa, and you can stay connected during your stay as Hotel Deccan Park offers guests free wifi.
The hotel features a 24 hour front desk, 24 hour check-in, and a concierge. Plus, Hotel Deccan Park offers breakfast, providing a pleasant respite from your busy day. For guests with a vehicle, free parking is available.
Travelers looking for a place to eat close to Hotel Deccan Park can head to Sri Venkateshwara Bakers (0.2 mi), Deccan Spice (0.4 mi), or Food Land (0.1 mi), all of which are within walking distance.
We’re sure you’ll enjoy your stay at Hotel Deccan Park as you experience everything Hyderabad has to offer.
